<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">

<style>
@page {
    size: A4;
    margin: 25mm 20mm 25mm 20mm;
}

body {
    font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #222;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: right;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
}

.section {
    margin-top: 25px;
}

.header-table {
    width: 100%;
}

.header-left {
    width: 60%;
    vertical-align: top;
}

.header-right {
    width: 40%;
    text-align: right;
    vertical-align: top;
}

.meta-table {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
}

.meta-table td {
    padding: 2px 6px;
}

.client-box {
    margin-top: 30px;
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    width: 60%;
}

.invoice-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 30px;
}

.invoice-table th {
    border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
    padding: 8px 5px;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 12px;
}

.invoice-table td {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 6px 5px;
}

.right {
    text-align: right;
}

.totals {
    width: 40%;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-top: 20px;
    border-collapse: collapse;
}

.totals td {
    padding: 6px;
}

.totals tr:last-child td {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 14px;
    border-top: 2px solid #333;
}

.footer {
    margin-top: 40px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #555;
}

.small {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #666;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<table class="header-table">
<tr>
<td class="header-left">
    <strong>{{ config.legal_name }}</strong><br>
    {{ config.address }}<br>
    {{ config.postal_code }} {{ config.city }}<br>
    {{ config.country }}<br><br>
    SIRET: {{ config.siret }}<br>
    {{ invoice.vat_notice }}
</td>

<td class="header-right">
    <h1>FACTURE</h1>
    <table class="meta-table">
        <tr>
            <td><strong>N°</strong></td>
            <td>{{ invoice.invoice_number }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Date</strong></td>
            <td>{{ invoice.issue_date }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Échéance</strong></td>
            <td>{{ invoice.due_date }}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>

<!-- CLIENT -->
<div class="client-box">
<strong>Facturé à :</strong><br>
{{ invoice.client.LegalName }}<br>
{{ invoice.client.Address }}<br>
{{ invoice.client.PostalCode }} {{ invoice.client.City }}<br>
{{ invoice.client.Country }}
</div>

<!-- LINES -->
<table class="invoice-table">
<tr>
    <th>Description</th>
    <th class="right">Qté</th>
    <th class="right">Prix unitaire</th>
    <th class="right">Total</th>
</tr>

{% for line in invoice.lines %}
<tr>
    <td>{{ line.description }}</td>
    <td class="right">{{ line.quantity }}</td>
    <td class="right">{{ "%.2f"|format(line.unit_price) }} {{ invoice.currency }}</td>
    <td class="right">{{ "%.2f"|format(line.total) }} {{ invoice.currency }}</td>
</tr>
{% endfor %}
</table>

<!-- TOTALS -->
<table class="totals">
<tr>
    <td>Total HT</td>
    <td class="right">{{ "%.2f"|format(invoice.total) }} {{ invoice.currency }}</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>TVA</td>
    <td class="right">0.00 {{ invoice.currency }}</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Total TTC</td>
    <td class="right">{{ "%.2f"|format(invoice.total) }} {{ invoice.currency }}</td>
</tr>
</table>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<div class="footer">
Paiement à {{ config.payment_terms_days }} jours.<br>
Merci d’indiquer le numéro de facture lors du paiement.<br><br>

<span class="small">
Conformément à l’article L441-10 du Code de commerce, des pénalités de retard sont exigibles 
en cas de paiement après la date d’échéance.
</span>
</div>

</body>
</html>
